This license governs the use of the InsightSpike-AI software and associated models (the "Software"), a revolutionary analogical reasoning and insight detection system.

PREAMBLE
This technology represents a significant advancement in machine understanding and analogical reasoning, capable of generating insights across domains. With such power comes responsibility. This license is designed to promote beneficial uses while preventing harmful applications.

1. GRANT OF RIGHTS
Subject to your compliance with this license, you are granted a non-exclusive, worldwide, non-transferable, royalty-free, revocable license to use, reproduce, modify, and distribute the Software for the permitted purposes outlined below.

2. PERMITTED USES
✅ The following uses are explicitly permitted:
- Academic research and scientific study
- Educational purposes and classroom demonstrations  
- Non-commercial personal projects and experimentation
- Healthcare and medical research (non-harmful)
- Environmental sustainability and climate research
